active.description: The active state of the control. This is typically used to highlight components.
active.description_zh: 控制项的 active 状态。这通常用于高亮显示组件。

append-icon.description: Creates a v-icon component after default content in the append slot.
append-icon.description_zh: 在追加槽中的默认内容之后创建 v 图标组件。

block.description: Expands the button to 100% of the available space.
block.description_zh: 将按钮扩大到可用空间的 100％。

border.description: Applies a border style to the component.

color.description: Applies specified color to the control - supports utility colors (for example success or purple) or css color (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). Find a list of built-in classes on the colors page.
color.description_zh: 将指定颜色应用于控件 - 支持实用颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 css 颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 css 颜色（#033 或 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)）。 在颜色页面上查找内置类的列表。

density.description: Adjust the vertical height used by the component.
density.description_zh: 调整组件使用的垂直高度。

disabled.description: Remove click or target functionality from the component.
disabled.description_zh: 移除组件的单击或 target 功能。

elevation.description: The component's elevation accepts values between 0 and 24. You can browse more information on the elevation page.
elevation.description_zh: 组件的海拔可接受 0 到 24 之间的值。你可以在 elevation page 浏览更多信息。

exact.description: Exact match link. Without this link, '/' will match every route. You can view more exact props in the vue-router documentation.
exact.description_zh: 完全匹配链接。如果没有这个链接，‘/’ 将匹配每个路由。你能够在 vue-router 文档浏览更多 exact prop。

flat.description: Removes the button box shadow. This is different than using the ‘flat’ variant.
flat.description_zh: 删除按钮框阴影。 这与使用“扁平”变体不同。

height.description: Set the height of the component.

href.description: Designate the component as the anchor and apply the href attribute.
href.description_zh: 指定组件为锚点并应用 href 属性。

icon.description: Apply a specific icon using the v-icon component. The button will become round.
icon.description_zh: 使用 v-icon 组件应用特定图标。 按钮将变成圆形。

loading.description: Displays linear progress bar. Can either be a String which specifies which color is applied to the progress bar (any material color or theme color - primary, secondary, success, info, warning, error) or a Boolean which uses the component color (set by color prop - if it’s supported by the component) or the primary color.
loading.description_zh: 显示线性进度条。 可以是指定应用于进度条的颜色的字符串（任何材质颜色或主题颜色 - 主要、次要、成功、信息、警告、错误）或使用组件颜色的布尔值（由 color 属性设置 - 如果 它由组件支持）或原色。

location.description: Specifies the component’s location. Can combine by using a space separated string.
location.description_zh: 指定组件的位置。 可以使用空格分隔的字符串进行组合。

max-height.description: Set the maximum height of the component.

max-width.description: Set the maximum width of the component.

min-height.description: Set the minimum height of the component.

min-width.description: Set the minimum width of the component.

position.description: Sets the position for the component.

prepend-icon.description: Creates a v-icon component in the prepend slot before default content.
prepend-icon.description_zh: 在默认内容之前的前置槽中创建 v 图标组件。

replace.description: Setting replace prop will call router.replace() instead of router.push() when clicked, so the navigation will not leave a history record. You can find more information about the replace prop on the vue-router documentation.
replace.description_zh: 设置replace属性将在点击时调用router.replace()而不是router.push()，因此导航不会留下历史记录。 您可以在 vue-router 文档中找到有关替换属性的更多信息。

rounded.description: Applies the border-radius style to the specified component. You can get more information about this on the Border Corner Radius page
rounded.description_zh: 对指定的组件应用 border-radius 样式。您可以在 边框的圆角半径页面 获取更多有关信息

selected-class.description: Configure the CSS class name to be applied when the selected item is selected.
selected-class.description_zh: 配置被选中项目时应用的 CSS 类名。

size.description: Set the height and width of the component. The default unit is px. The following predefined sizes are also available: x-small, small, default, large, and x-large.
size.description_zh: 设置组件的高度和宽度。默认单位是px。也可以使用以下预定义的大小：x-small、small、default、large和x-large。

stacked.description: Display this button as a flex-column
stacked.description_zh: 以 flex-column 形式显示此按钮

symbol.description: The Symbol used to hook into group functionality for components like v-btn-toggle and v-bottom-navigation.
symbol.description_zh: 该符号用于挂钩 v-btn-toggle 和 v-bottom-navigation 等组件的组功能。

tag.description: Specifies a custom tag to use on the root element.
tag.description_zh: 指定在根元素上使用的自定义标签。

theme.description: Specify a theme for this component and all of its children.
theme.description_zh: 指定该组件及其所有子组件的主题。

to.description: Represents the target route of the link. You can browse more to props in the vue-router documentation.
to.description_zh: 表示链接的目标路由。你可以在 vue-router 文档浏览更多 to prop。

value.description: The value used when selecting components within the group. If not provided, a unique ID is used.
value.description_zh: 在组中选择组件时使用的值。如果没有提供，则使用唯一 ID。

variant.description: Applies a distinct style to the component.
variant.description_zh: 对组件应用独特的样式。

width.description: Set the width of the component.
